biosecLogger.analysis

Class Result

  • java.lang.Object
    • biosecLogger.analysis.Result

  • public class Result
extends java.lang.Object
    Result class contains individual FAR and FRR per user, total FAR and FRR. It is supposed to show and store analyzed results.
    Author:
    Stefan Smihla
